  "title": "CNC Programmers",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duties</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Create CNC programs, plan tooling &amp; fixture for Mill &amp; Turn machining</li>\n  <li>Generate routing processes in ERP system</li>\n  <li>Estimate machining cycle time each routing processes</li>\n  <li>Perform technical planning and specification of the production process</li>\n  <li>Production schedule, loading &amp; capacity</li>\n  <li>Liaise with customers for technical and specification require</li>\n  <li>Establish PMP (Process Management Plan) as per customer requirements</li>\n  <li>Analyze existing capacity &amp; resources and propose for optimizing utilization</li>\n  <li>Technical support for daily manufacturing process including design jig &amp; fixtures</li>\n  <li>Review existing processes and establish the best machining processes</li>\n  <li>Propose new ideas for continuous improvement</li>\n  <li>Mastercam / Solid cam </li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min. 5 years experience in a manufacturing environment, preferably in precision Engineering</li>\n  <li>Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma/Post Graduate Diploma in Mechanical /Manufacturing Engineering field preferred</li>\n  <li>Strong in technical skill and able to read mechanical drawing</li>\n  <li>Possess knowledge of CNC &amp; CAD programming, Solidwork/Solidcam, Mastercam</li>\n  <li>In-depth knowledge of machining processes</li>\n  <li>Efficient in Microsoft Office</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently and as a team</li>\n  <li>Handles multi-tasking and stress well</li>\n</ul>",
